:1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"致一眾和理非：<br />\n上唔到前線，做到嘅就係文宣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:31:36.000Z","msg":"左膠：做文宣都係勇武手足，我會精神支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"幫手貼，路過停低寫下memo紙之類好基本<br />\n遲啲文宣都冇埋都唔知勇武可以點幫和理非<br />\n<br />\n睇到既和理非手足記住一樣野就足夠<br />\n只需要一樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好懶，唔好諗住有人做，自己就唔去做</span>"},{"pid":"524a5dd2b98ee71a6f93a2f7657b6415a022e1c6","tid":1821174,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a2d29d36bc924504943dd9c2ce7291d3c04b22","tid":1821174,"uid":225437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"中學生本身就唔應該上前線<br />\n上前線應該成年人既責任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"成年人罷工都唔敢 講經咩"},{"pid":"c01b5f6d7d5141230adfa76c36ad777987739478","tid":1821174,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"其實我同啲手足直頭教大家print落貼紙<br />\n仲出埋示範 但超級難推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出到第4個post 啦～你認同嘅話就入嚟支持吓我哋啦～<br />\n---------------------<br />\n[行動]連儂/文宣都可以十八區開花! A4 label周圍貼! 大量現成圖-即print 即貼(2)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1819022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1819022</a>"},{"pid":"0cb3967531451b55e0c580597bbc89a7c2b1b9b0","tid":1821174,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dcbe781a374934fdf817259414c0500711d86c9","tid":1821174,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"他與爸爸同來，一個噴膠，一個貼紙。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"其實我同啲手足直頭教大家print落貼紙<br />\n仲出埋示範 但超級難推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c